          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-1" n="1">The Suit which humbly You have made</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-2" n="2">Is fully and Maturely weigh'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-3" n="3">«LD»And as 'tis Your Petition:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-4" n="4">I do Forgive for well I know</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-5" n="5">Since You're so Bruis'd another Blow</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-6" n="6">«LD»Wou'd Break the Head of Priscian.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-7" n="7">'Tis not my Purpose or Intent</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-8" n="8">That You shou'd suffer Banishment,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-9" n="9">«LD»I Pardon, now You've Courted</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-10" n="10">And Yet I fear this Clemency</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-11" n="11">Will come too late to profit thee</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-12" n="12">«LD»For You're with Grief Transported.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-13" n="13">However this I do Command</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-14" n="14">That You Your Birch do take in hand</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-15" n="15">«LD»Read Concord and Syntax-on;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-16" n="16">The Bays You own are onely Mine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-17" n="17">Do You then still Your Nouns Decline</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-18" n="18">«LD»Since You've declin'd────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-19" n="19">«LD»Dan: Jackson.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06B002D-line-20" n="20">om.</l>
          </lg>
